    <h1>Our Mission</h1>
    <p class="lead" style="text-align: center;">Aid the Homeless by distributing Turtle Shelter Vests
      <br>
      <br>
      Turtle Shelter Vests are a high tech but simple solution to help save lives. They act as 
      a portable "shelter" anyone can carry with them, just like a turtle.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="content">
    <h1>What You Can Do</h1>
    <p class="lead" style="text-align: center;">We are very grateful for anyone that desires to help this project progress! We have two main ways to help.
      <br>
      <br>
      <b>1.</b> You could request an event to make Turtle Shelter Vests which will be distributed throughout your community. These events are customizable depending on your venue size, skill level of attendees, length and more! Click the link above to get started.
      <br>
      <br>
      <b>2.</b>You can also sign up to become a 'Volunteer'. At every event we try and have 1 volunteer for every 10-15 attendees. Volunteers help with setup, cleanup, and assisting attendees with the vest making process. We will contact with events in your location and you are able to accept or decline any invitation depending on your availability. Click the link above to get started.
      <br>
      <br>
      If you are not able to give your time you are also welcome to donate to the cause! Every dollar helps us to continue to provide these vests to those in need.
    </p>
    <p class="lead" style="text-align: center;">
      More information about these vests can be found on our <a href="/About/ourTech">Our Tech</a> page.
    </p>
  </div>
